name: Unfinished Open Worl Game
description:
TO PLAY: Go into the folder "Unfinished Open Worl Game", then "UOWG Build", then open "Unfinished Open Worl Game.exe".

yo this is a private link for bee bun and mcsmooth ONLY! If you aren't one of those people... how the flup did you get this link? Get outta hereeeee ;)

hope you have good fun and a laugh! I think it's a pretty fun and funny experience <3!!

REVISED DESCRIPTION:

Hi, Jamer here. Don't worry, ignore the above description. You likely aren't Bee, Bunni or McSmooth.

While playing this game, keep in mind I only used assets from other people.

Also keep in mind the game is unrefined, and I did not attempt to refine it.

There will be notes in the game that aren't directed towards you; because originally, I was just going to send the game to three people.

Since that is no longer the case, I'm putting it out publicly. The game is open source: you can do whatever you like with it.

Have a wonderful day.
